prompts.prompt: In a distant galaxy far away, there lived a curious elephant named N. N loved to explore the vastness of space, floating among the stars and planets, feeling the gentle pull of gravity guiding them through the cosmic dance.

One day, as N was exploring a mysterious asteroid belt, they encountered a swirling vortex of water in the vacuum of space. N was intrigued by this unusual sight and decided to investigate. As they approached the water, they realized it was a portal to another dimension.

Without hesitation, N plunged into the watery portal, feeling weightless and free as they danced through the liquid universe. After a thrilling journey, N emerged on the other side, back in their familiar galaxy. They had learned that sometimes the greatest adventures can be found in the most unexpected places.
